1999-09-16  Mikio Nakajima  <minakaji@osaka.email.ne.jp>

	* experimental/skk-tutcdef.el: Apply patch
	of14294.63921.879835.8921F@osaka.email.ne.jp.
	
	* SKK-CFG: Add `SKK-MK-cleanup-trouble-makers' entry.

